{"type":"article","id":16871,"title":"【突发】黑皮互殴：湖北黄梅交警VS江西九江特警(更新官方回应)","uid":18252,"topics":[6338,5262,2885,2645,5930,2030],"contents":"事情起因据说是湖北黄梅县打开关卡之后，交界的江西九江市跑到湖北境内的长江大桥一头设卡禁止湖北人入内。黄梅县交警与九江的警察理论，结果一个人被九江10几个警察围殴，引发桥上民众不满，出现了警车被打翻的高雅画面。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/erhjM1H.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/erhjM1H.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/erhjM1H.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/urVpL8v.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/urVpL8v.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/urVpL8v.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n黄梅县县委书记和九江市市委书记前往现场调解。说是上面会协商，打人的事会依法追究。目前九江的关卡已经打开。有大量湖北民众到九江市黑皮大队门口高呼“道歉”<br>\n<br>\n视频集（几十个视频，顺序好像有点乱。请大家慢慢观看）：<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Elizabeth1989zz/status/1243452726027137024\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Elizabeth1989zz/status/1243452726027137024</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fiteray/status/1243460993469968385\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fiteray/status/1243460993469968385</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fiteray/status/1243457179887095808\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fiteray/status/1243457179887095808</a><br>\n<br>\n微博上也有很多视频和讨论，评论里基本就是湖北地域黑vs江西地域黑<br>\n<br>\n九江方面的通告解释（未FC）：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/4MIgxyG.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4MIgxyG.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/4MIgxyG.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hZzBkWo.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hZzBkWo.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hZzBkWo.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n据传是半官方解释（未FC）：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9foAQyF.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer